---
title: One-Pot Sausage and Orzo Stew with Garlic Bread
description: This one pot Italian orzo stew will whisk you off to the Italian countryside with flavours reminiscent of Nonna's kitchen. The slow-cooked flavours of sausage, crushed tomatoes and basil all come together in only 20 mins!
